<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>CEUNAK KHA RUN THLAH TUAH CH411</title>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Sualmui lakah na mi vialte kha an tang, Ceunak kha, (ceunak kha) run
 thlah tuah; (run thlah tuah) Khamhnak an herh na in an kaltak dih cang,
 Khamhnak chung, (Khamhnak chung) au than hna.

[C1]
   Maw Pathian, (Maw Pathian, sualnak a) sual a kan thlah piaktu, (kan
   thlahpiaktu) Khua zakip mi au hna law,(au hna law); Na hmaiah (Na hmaika
   ah) kun cio ko hna sehlaw, (kun cio ko hna sehlaw) Zungzal nang thangthat
   awkah. (Zungzal nang thangthat awkah.)

[V2]
 Na phung-chimtu nih an halpiak hna nak kha, Run ngai law (Run ngai
 law) bawm tuah han; (bawm tuah hna) An sual hremnak chungin an luat khawh
 nakhnga, Ceunak kha (ceunak kha) run thlah tuah.

[C2]
   Maw Pathian, (Maw Pathian, sualnak a) sual a kan thlah piaktu, (kan
   thlahpiaktu) Khua zakip mi au hna law,(au hna law); Na hmaiah (Na hmaika
   ah) kun cio ko hna sehlaw, (kun cio ko hna sehlaw) Zungzal nang thangthat
   awkah. (Zungzal nang thangthat awkah.)

[V3]
 Jesuh vel kha mi vialte sinah phan seh, Ceunak kha (ceunak kha) run
 thlah tuah; (run thlah tuah) Khrih ruahnak bantuk an ngeih khawh cio
 nakhnga, Ceunak kha (ceunak kha) run thlah tuah.

[C3]
   Maw Pathian, (Maw Pathian, sualnak a) sual a kan thlah piaktu, (kan
   thlahpiaktu) Khua zakip mi au hna law,(au hna law); Na hmaiah (Na hmaika
   ah) kun cio ko hna sehlaw, (kun cio ko hna sehlaw) Zungzal nang thangthat
   awkah. (Zungzal nang thangthat awkah.)</lyrics>
<hymn_number>411</hymn_number>
</song>